Package: libclastfm0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Unofficial C-API to the Last.fm web service
 libclastfm is an unofficial C-API for the Last.fm web service 
 written with libcurl. libclastfm supports much more than 
 basic scrobble submission. You can send shouts, fetch album covers 
 and much more.

Package: libclastfm0-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libclastfm0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: libclastfm development headers
 libclastfm is an unofficial C-API for the Last.fm web service 
 written with libcurl. libclastfm supports much more than 
 basic scrobble submission. You can send shouts, fetch album covers 
 and much more.
 .
 (This package contains the header files)
